&thinsp;ㄌㆲˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>是<rt>&thinsp;ㄒ丨˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>伊<rt>&thinsp;丨&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>不<rt>&thinsp;ㆬ˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby>(/伓)<ruby>好<rt>&thinsp;ㄏㄜˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>，<ruby>汝<rt>&thinsp;ㄌ丨ˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>著<rt>&thinsp;ㄉ丨ㄜㆷ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>(/<ruby>都<rt>&thinsp;ㄉㄜ˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby>)<ruby>一<rt>&thinsp;ㄐ丨ㆵ̇&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>點<rt>&thinsp;ㄉ丨ㆰˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>責<rt>&thinsp;ㄐ丨ㆤㆶ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>任<rt>&thinsp;ㆢ丨ㆬ˫/ㄌ丨ㆬ˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>著<rt>&thinsp;ㄉ丨ㄜㆷ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>(/<ruby>都<rt>&thinsp;ㄉㄜ˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby>)<ruby>無<rt>&thinsp;ㆠㄜˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>？句形：<ruby>連<rt>&thinsp;ㄌ丨ㄢˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>……<ruby>都<rt>&thinsp;ㄉㄡ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>……/……<ruby>都<rt>&thinsp;ㄉㄡ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>……①例：連我～/也不知道。<ruby>連<rt>&thinsp;ㄌ丨ㄢˊ→ㄌ丨ㄢ˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>我<rt>&thinsp;ㆣㄨㄚˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>著<rt>&thinsp;ㄉ丨ㄜㆷ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>(/<ruby>都<rt>&thinsp;ㄉㄜ˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby>)(/<mark>&#xffaca;</mark>/<ruby>亦<rt>&thinsp;ㄇㄚ˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby>)<ruby>不<rt>&thinsp;ㆬ˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby>(/伓)<ruby>知<rt>&thinsp;ㄗㄞ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。②例：連一根針掉在地下～聽得見。<ruby>連<rt>&thinsp;ㄌ丨ㄢˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>一<rt>&thinsp;ㄐ丨ㆵ̇&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>枝<rt>&thinsp;ㄍ丨&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>針<rt>&thinsp;ㄗㆰ/ㄐ丨ㆰ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>加<rt>&thinsp;ㄍㄚ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>(/下)<ruby>落<rt>&thinsp;ㄌㄠㆷ̇&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>落<rt>&thinsp;ㄌㄜㆷ̇&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>塗<rt>&thinsp;ㄊㆦˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>骹<rt>&thinsp;ㄎㄚ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>著<rt>&thinsp;ㄉ丨ㄜㆷ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>(/<ruby>都<rt>&thinsp;ㄉㄜ˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby>)(/<mark>&#xffaca;</mark>/<ruby>亦<rt>&thinsp;ㄇㄚ˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby>)<ruby>有<rt>&thinsp;ㄨ˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聽<rt>&thinsp;ㄊ丨ㆩ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>見<rt>&thinsp;ㄍㆳ˪&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。③例：連小孩子～搬得動。
